I'm gonna steal this picture
right out from under your nose,

44:54.893 --> 44:56.159
and you know I can do it.

44:56.161 --> 44:58.194
Are you threatening me?

44:58.196 --> 44:59.896
Bette and Joan.

44:59.898 --> 45:01.964
